  <heading>SQXTUNB</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Signed saturating extract narrow to unsigned integer (bottom)</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction saturates the signed integer value in each source element to an unsigned
integer value that is half the original source element width, and places
the results in the even-numbered half-width destination
elements, while setting the odd-numbered elements
to zero.</para>
    </authored>
    <predicated>False</predicated>
  </desc>
